<h2>perturb: Tools for Evaluating Collinearity</h2>
<p>Use the perturb() function to evaluates collinearity by adding 
    random noise to selected variables (Hendrickx &amp; Pelzer 2004). The colldiag 
    function() calculates condition numbers and variance decomposition proportions 
    to test for collinearity and uncover its sources (Belsley 1980).</p>
